text: Dionne Julia Bromfield (born 1 February 1996) is an English singer, songwriter, TV presenter, and television personality. She rose to fame in 2009 signing to Amy Winehouse's record label Lioness Records. == References == Category:1996 births Category:British R&B; musicians Category:Black British musicians Category:English songwriters Category:Singers from London Category:People from the London Borough of Tower Hamlets Category:Living people Category:English musicians
